    <title>RxCAP Act of 2017</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Reducing Existing Costs Associated with Pharmaceuticals for Seniors Act of 2017 or the RxCAP Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to eliminate beneficiary cost-sharing above the Medicare prescription benefit's annual out-of-pocket threshold beginning in plan year 2018. Under current law, the Medicare prescription drug benefit provides coverage above that threshold only with cost-sharing in the form of either copayment or coinsurance. </p>]]></text>
